<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Course Rejection Notification</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; padding: 20px; } .container { background: #fff;
      padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); } h1 { color: #d9534f; border-bottom: 2px solid #d9534f;
      padding-bottom: 10px; } ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <h1>Course Rejection</h1>
      <p>Dear {{{firstname}}} {{{lastname}}},</p>
      <p>We regret to inform you that your course submission for "{{{title}}}" has been <strong>rejected</strong>. Here are some reasons why:</p>
      <ul>
        {{#each reasons}}
          <li>{{this}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
      <p>We appreciate your interest in contributing to our platform. Please consider the feedback provided to enhance your proposal for future
        submissions.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br />
        The Neargami Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>